Shag Thomas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shag_Thomas 0 Shag Thomas (born James Thomas, August 11, 1924 – July 25, 1982) was an American professional wrestler during the 1950s and 1960s. He was one of the few African-American wrestlers of his day. Shag_Thomas ( born James_Thomas , August_11_,_1924 – July_25_,_1982 ) was an_American_professional_wrestler during the_1950s_and_1960s .
